  "title": "switch用のソフトはswich2に差して使える",
  "created": 1777987116,
  "updated": 1777987243,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f9ee2bf769734bdf8bb638",
      "text": "switch用のソフトはswich2に差して使える",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987116,
      "updated": 1777987139
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee4d0000000000ce5d54",
      "text": "ただし、一部ソフトでは動作確認で問題が見つかっているものもある",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987149,
      "updated": 1777987226
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee9a0000000000ce5d57",
      "text": "[https://www.nintendo.com/jp/hardware/switch2/compatibility/index.html ここ]で調べられる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987226,
      "updated": 1777987239
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee600000000000ce5d56",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987169,
      "updated": 1777987169
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee2b0000000000ce5d4b",
      "text": "from [2026/05/05]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987116,
      "updated": 1777987116
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee2b0000000000ce5d4c",
      "text": "switch用のソフトってswich2に刺せば普通に使えるんだろうか",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987116,
      "updated": 1777987116
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee2b0000000000ce5d4d",
      "text": " ほい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987116,
      "updated": 1777987116
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee2b0000000000ce5d4e",
      "text": " [https://www.nintendo.com/jp/hardware/switch2/compatibility/index.html Nintendo Switch 2 とNintendo Switchの互換性について | Nintendo]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987116,
      "updated": 1777987116
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee2b0000000000ce5d4f",
      "text": "  大感謝！[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987116,
      "updated": 1777987116
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee2b0000000000ce5d50",
      "text": "  基本的には遊べるのか",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777987116,
      "updated": 1777987116
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ee2b0000000000ce5d51",
      "text": "   問題が見つかっている場合はそのソフトのページに書いてあるっぽい",
